Uses of Package
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.model

Packages that use com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.model 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.command
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.command is a group of services which only mutate data but have not advanced query functionalities.
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.controller
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the enterprise service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the information state.
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.dto
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.dto.annotation  
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.helper
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.helper is a group of static utility methods to convert the entity object to the dto representation and to authorize a user.
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.model
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.model contains all entities from the enterprise service database and the enum declarations.
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.query
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.repository
com.mhealthatlas.enterpriseapps.repository contains all repository interfaces of the enterprise service.
